&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Project:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Where Winds Meet&lt;/em&gt; is an epic open-world action-adventure RPG rooted in the rich legacy of Wuxia.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Set during the turbulent era of tenth-century China, you take on the role of a young sword master, uncovering forgotten truths and the mysteries of your own identity.&lt;/p&gt;
