&lt;li&gt;Monitor competitor and industry social channels to identify best practices and content opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support influencer and community-related initiatives as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Social Media Operations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with content calendar management, publishing coordination, and campaign tracking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the preparation of social media copy, screenshots, and other platform assets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help collect and organize performance data from social media campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the development and execution of localized social media initiatives for English-speaking audiences, ensuring content is culturally relevant, engaging, and aligned with community interests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review social content and community communications from a cultural sensitivity perspective, helping ensure messaging is appropriate and well received by audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Performance Analysis&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor content performance and engagement metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in preparing reports and identifying content trends, audience preferences, and optimization opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
