&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Currently pursuing or recently completed a Bachelor&#39;s degree in Marketing, Communications, Media, Business, Social Sciences or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Passion for video games, with a strong interest in action RPGs, open-world games, and online gaming communities. Familiarity with &lt;em&gt;Where Winds Meet&lt;/em&gt; or the Wuxia genre is highly desirable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;

